OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781453487
OL,3,C'It doesn't feel like home anymore':
OL,4,CRow over 200-year-old collapsing wall
OL,6,FA group of neighbours in Bristol say
OL,7,Fthey have been left feeling "like
OL,8,Fcriminals" because of a row with the
OL,9,Fcouncil over who should pay to repair
OL,10,Fan enormous 200-year-old wall.
OL,12,FThe residents say they have already
OL,13,Fbeen forced to spend thousands of
OL,14,Fpounds for temporary bollards and
OL,15,Ffences for the wall, which is at risk
OL,16,Fof collapsing onto one of the city's
OL,17,Fbusiest roads.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
