PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781453487
OL,3,C'It doesn't feel like home anymore':
OL,4,CRow over 200-year-old collapsing wall
OL,6,FBristol City Council insists it is the
OL,7,Fresidents' responsibility "to keep it
OL,8,Fsafe and secure" as it solely supports
OL,9,Ftheir gardens.
OL,11,FLouise Cinderby's home backs onto the
OL,12,Fwall on Rose Green Road. She has lived
OL,13,Fthere for more than twenty years but
OL,14,Fsays the two-year stand off has taken
OL,15,Fover her life.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781453487
OL,3,C'It doesn't feel like home anymore':
OL,4,CRow over 200-year-old collapsing wall
OL,6,FShe said: "I love living here. I love
OL,7,Fthis house. But right here now it
OL,8,Fdoesn't feel like home anymore. You
OL,9,Ffeel like you've become a criminal in
OL,10,Fyour own home, when it's not on your
OL,11,Fdeeds.
OL,13,F"We've done everything that we can but
OL,14,Fit feels like we've been forced into a
OL,15,Fcorner and where we don't actually
OL,16,Fknow what we should be doing anymore.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781453487
OL,3,C'It doesn't feel like home anymore':
OL,4,CRow over 200-year-old collapsing wall
OL,6,F"It's constantly there in the
OL,7,Fbackground. You look on your emails,
OL,8,Fyour post, what bills, are we going to
OL,9,Fget another letter from the debt
OL,10,Fcollectors?"
OL,12,FLouise claims the wall, which pre-
OL,13,Fdates the properties, does not feature
OL,14,Fany of her neighbours' deeds and
OL,15,Ftherefore they do not own it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
