FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781453487
OL,3,C'It doesn't feel like home anymore':
OL,4,CRow over 200-year-old collapsing wall
OL,6,FBristol City Council has written to
OL,7,Fthe owners of the properties asking
OL,8,Fthem to complete the repairs. They say
OL,9,Ftheir actions are supported by the
OL,10,FLocal Government and Social Care
OL,11,FOmbudsman.
OL,13,FTwo years on, nothing has been done to
OL,14,Fresolve the wall's condition.
OL,16,FThe council has installed bollards and
OL,17,Ffences around the wall and is
OL,18,Finvoicing the residents. They have now
OL,19,Fbeen in place for more than 18 months.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
