PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781453487
OL,3,C'It doesn't feel like home anymore':
OL,4,CRow over 200-year-old collapsing wall
OL,6,FNeighbour Russell Seymour says he's
OL,7,Fpaid around #1,700 to cover the costs
OL,8,Fof the safety measures.
OL,10,FRussell said: "If this had happened to
OL,11,Fme ten years ago I would be on the
OL,12,Ffloor now. My economic situation has
OL,13,Fmoved on a bit but getting an invoice
OL,14,Ffor #800 before Christmas...
OL,16,F"I paid it begrudgingly, I was worried
OL,17,Fabout debt collectors. I thought it
OL,18,Fmight be the start of a resolution.
OL,19,FBut nothing has happened."
OL,26,@rD@OOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
