PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781453487
OL,3,C'It doesn't feel like home anymore':
OL,4,CRow over 200-year-old collapsing wall
OL,6,FPreviously, Louise paid thousands of
OL,7,Fpounds in an attempt to repair the
OL,8,Fwall. She says she wanted to move on
OL,9,Ffrom the dispute, even though she did
OL,10,Fnot believe she owned the wall, but
OL,11,Fthe repair failed.
OL,13,FRussell and the other residents know
OL,14,Fthey may face having to pay
OL,15,Fconsiderably more.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
