OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781453487
OL,3,C'It doesn't feel like home anymore':
OL,4,CRow over 200-year-old collapsing wall
OL,6,FHe said: "I need to be able to plan
OL,7,Ffor the next couple of years and it
OL,8,Fseems that there will have to be some
OL,9,Fmoney spent on it one way or the
OL,10,Fother. It's just not knowing. It's
OL,11,Fbeen two years and no action has been
OL,12,Ftaken."
OL,14,FThe neighbours say they want an open
OL,15,Fdialogue with the council to discuss a
OL,16,Fplan going forward - whoever ends up
OL,17,Ffooting the bill.
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
