SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781453487
OL,3,C'It doesn't feel like home anymore':
OL,4,CRow over 200-year-old collapsing wall
OL,6,FCouncillor Ed Plowden, chair of the
OL,7,Ftransport and connectivity committee,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This section of a retaining
OL,9,Fwall along Rose Green Road, which
OL,10,Fsolely supports the private rear
OL,11,Fgardens of properties, is at risk of
OL,12,Fcollapsing and requires significant
OL,13,Frepairs to make it safe and ensure it
OL,14,Fisn't presenting a risk to people
OL,15,Fusing the road or pavement.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
