PN,40410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781453487
OL,3,C'It doesn't feel like home anymore':
OL,4,CRow over 200-year-old collapsing wall
OL,6,F"We are in contact with the residents
OL,7,Fand owners of the properties whose
OL,8,Fgardens are held up by this section of
OL,9,Fretaining wall and have been clear on
OL,10,Four position and what is required of
OL,11,Fthem to remove the risk.
OL,13,F"Although this position has been
OL,14,Fchallenged by residents, the council's
OL,15,Factions have been supported by the
OL,16,FLocal Government and Social Care
OL,17,FOmbudsman.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781453487
OL,3,C'It doesn't feel like home anymore':
OL,4,CRow over 200-year-old collapsing wall
OL,6,F"Where any structure, such as a wall,
OL,7,Fbridge or subway, is identified as
OL,8,Fpresenting a risk to people using a
OL,9,Fpublic road or pavement the council
OL,10,Fwill take action to ensure safety
OL,11,Fmeasures are in place to address the
OL,12,Frisk.
OL,14,F"This may include closing the pavement
OL,15,For road and providing an alternative
OL,16,Fpedestrian or vehicle route and
OL,17,Fensuring a structural support is place
OL,18,Funtil repairs have been completed and
OL,19,Fthe structure is no longer in a
OL,20,Fdangerous condition.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
